messages.message:
Hey team, how does AIHub know which projects to show on the homepage? Before I started recording this, I was trying to find out how to find the recently edited projects from my homepage but I didn't see anything. Only after I went to workspaces was I able to see it

NOTE: this is also on my development environment but these projects were also recent so I was expecting them to show up
should be recently accessed, but i believe this information is only persisted in FE local storage CC: @Weiming Wu
